{"tid":707132,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【睇波睇到唔想上機】釜山冇嘢玩。","createTime":"2018-06-18T12:29:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T05:49:20.000Z","uid":37661,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4528c0186a7211fc8e354a2f83a3514f36c03ba8","tid":707132,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T12:29:22.000Z","msg":"喺韓國睇特别興奮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/202801_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2F202801_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d05aa5a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba8d1d737cc35637f7524d398624241df9935783","tid":707132,"uid":168430,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T02:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我尋晚都係釜山睇<br />\n韓國人支持自己隊真係好正"},{"pid":"2c1b003415d22e15fa36278ae72fbc3d66d357ad","tid":707132,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba8d1d737cc35637f7524d398624241df9935783","tid":707132,"uid":168430,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T02:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我尋晚都係釜山睇<br />\n韓國人支持自己隊真係好正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T03:00:22.000Z","msg":"我住間 Hostel 貼晒紙講場波個時間<br />\n<br />\n可惜我噚晚就走，機場啲友都有大叫。<br />\n<br />\n第一次攻門頂頭鎚出界嗰次。"},{"pid":"f1d3ac76b2fec57bb3164bf03b195fc310d02bb6","tid":707132,"uid":47041,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T03:43:12.000Z","msg":"岩呀<br />\n韓狗輸波我都特別開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/red.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/red.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/red.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6a5deebe514484fa2626634ba17afb31ccec69a","tid":707132,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T03:44:38.000Z","msg":"端午節去釜山，除咗食，乜都無 Plan。<br />\n<br />\n坐時間最靚又最辛苦既釜山航空，香港零晨兩點幾飛，到釜山朝早六點幾，回程釜山夜晚九點半機，飛到香港零晨十二點，玩足3日唔洗請假。<br />\n<br />\n上年搭嗰架機，腳位好鬆動，呢次就窄好多，搞到喺機上唔好瞓，又唔記得拎頸枕出嚟，寄咗倉。<br />\n<br />\n夜機得一杯嘢飲同埋一個蛋糕。<br />\n<br />\n飛到釜山。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/114126_c43f98a1db7081ec82ed3fcaa4f0cf5e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F114126_c43f98a1db7081ec82ed3fcaa4f0cf5e.jpg&h=99ca2f24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/114126_a8278cbc168f40188c4e3938f1ee002a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F114126_a8278cbc168f40188c4e3938f1ee002a.jpg&h=983f2155&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/114126_84665bef2637ccde4da7fb874dc7140a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F114126_84665bef2637ccde4da7fb874dc7140a.jpg&h=e6ae4e4a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8522251a0bd9b5c7610422e98ec90e2c9bf6590b","tid":707132,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T03:52:34.000Z","msg":"上次住西浦，呢次住海雲臺。<br />\n<br />\n落機例牌排晒長龍，不過叫做唔算太耐，因為分咗幾條韓國櫃檯俾其他旅客。<br />\n<br />\n本身有韓幣同 T-Money 卡坐車，電話卡喺鴨記買埋，喺機場乜都無搞就直接走。<br />\n<br />\n坐單軌車出沙上，再轉地鐵，去韓國一定要用 T-Money 卡，要轉車係可以慳好多。<br />\n<br />\n我由機場去到海雲臺只係 2000won。<br />\n<br />\n第一步就食早餐，揀咗間開廿四小時既舒暢鱈魚湯，不過我真係勁攰，人哋可以好快食完，我就乜都無乜郁過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/114803_9a14dc112657bf21b8724e68a04f900e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F114803_9a14dc112657bf21b8724e68a04f900e.jpg&h=67b40492&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/114803_61d355c9741f6c806421a86a70e493ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F114803_61d355c9741f6c806421a86a70e493ba.jpg&h=019727a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/114803_29648e18034f2bd8ac26d4e47a2f5c9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F114803_29648e18034f2bd8ac26d4e47a2f5c9b.jpg&h=4cead6ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n11000won 的鱈魚湯<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/114802_8a871eb645e2d97833508db3be71c722.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F114802_8a871eb645e2d97833508db3be71c722.jpg&h=f13ed78a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7000won 的蛋卷 (吔咗3件就收咗皮)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/114802_0d1b63538f3265b15d847f25a5ec9622.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F114802_0d1b63538f3265b15d847f25a5ec9622.jpg&h=67a5b32e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae13e0a2d8731f4932dff8cbb9e890e460642472","tid":707132,"uid":168430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c1b003415d22e15fa36278ae72fbc3d66d357ad","tid":707132,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba8d1d737cc35637f7524d398624241df9935783","tid":707132,"uid":168430,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T02:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我尋晚都係釜山睇<br />\n韓國人支持自己隊真係好正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T03:00:22.000Z","msg":"我住間 Hostel 貼晒紙講場波個時間<br />\n<br />\n可惜我噚晚就走，機場啲友都有大叫。<br />\n<br />\n第一次攻門頂頭鎚出界嗰次。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:04:49.000Z","msg":"輸十二碼果時<br />\n條韓妹（婆？）<br />\n係咁打鳩條仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5de105c3eae4f7cd37e78fc1d8e38f5413af8f9","tid":707132,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae13e0a2d8731f4932dff8cbb9e890e460642472","tid":707132,"uid":168430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c1b003415d22e15fa36278ae72fbc3d66d357ad","tid":707132,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba8d1d737cc35637f7524d398624241df9935783","tid":707132,"uid":168430,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T02:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我尋晚都係釜山睇<br />\n韓國人支持自己隊真係好正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T03:00:22.000Z","msg":"我住間 Hostel 貼晒紙講場波個時間<br />\n<br />\n可惜我噚晚就走，機場啲友都有大叫。<br />\n<br />\n第一次攻門頂頭鎚出界嗰次。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:04:49.000Z","msg":"輸十二碼果時<br />\n條韓妹（婆？）<br />\n係咁打鳩條仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:19:04.000Z","msg":"機場都有廢老嘈，話前面啲人唔好遮着部電視機。"},{"pid":"0dd88553a8b385c62c475b039d1ebbc3165fad09","tid":707132,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:32:55.000Z","msg":"揀咗海雲臺的 Canvas Hostel <br />\n<br />\n地鐵近冬柏站多過海雲臺站，行過去都算近。<br />\n<br />\n主大樓，Check in Check out 同食早餐都係呢度，呢度地下仲有 locker 可以放26吋喼入去，不過要自己帶鎖，但呢無24 小時 reception，要注意入住時間，早上退房門卡可以放 key box。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/122209_f83a3293510ea2fff5d5149b7cbfda79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F122209_f83a3293510ea2fff5d5149b7cbfda79.jpg&h=9b3a26bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主大樓的 Pantry 可煮食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/122209_5311fad44e69d9935f37791b1590f7c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F122209_5311fad44e69d9935f37791b1590f7c4.jpg&h=03ba0027&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/122209_2703f9f44cc450e283f0a3b861c8cc0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F122209_2703f9f44cc450e283f0a3b861c8cc0b.jpg&h=d2ef1d23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一個住宿大樓，地下有餐廳，住客亦可以在裡面享用自己食物，房間內是嚴禁飲食。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/122208_4bfcf461d5ce085df85cdcacfb3daab2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F122208_4bfcf461d5ce085df85cdcacfb3daab2.jpg&h=2313a5ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/122208_cd259c79b1c2a9e766136d786193671d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F122208_cd259c79b1c2a9e766136d786193671d.jpg&h=dc4450b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/122208_b942b3e2c50521850c8c30b4bc0bb316.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F122208_b942b3e2c50521850c8c30b4bc0bb316.jpg&h=d908a1ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n房間，勁大，不過無電視睇波，不過部冷氣勁嘈，遙控得韓文，唔知係咪唔識set。<br />\n<br />\n得毛巾，洗頭水、護髮素、梘液。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/122208_e0f341f47214122af5eabe00d3dff8a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F122208_e0f341f47214122af5eabe00d3dff8a6.jpg&h=30046dfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/122209_d602b42f6cea538351e9b8c684c42f69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F122209_d602b42f6cea538351e9b8c684c42f69.jpg&h=91b5aa4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd503a61fba20770a096375a4d91df9aa455ba88","tid":707132,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T05:45:44.000Z","msg":"當時係未夠鐘可以 Check in ，只係將行李擺咗喺 Locker 就出咗去。<br />\n<br />\n先要到海雲臺市場附近換錢。<br />\n<br />\n本身上網查咗間叫 Minibox ，去到得番間叫 Money BOX，但釜山找換店真係唔多，唔似首爾咁成行成市，明碼實價標晒出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/133722_198e929d8822205285129adbed856d7c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F133722_198e929d8822205285129adbed856d7c.jpg&h=0b148fcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/133721_bc303cbf9fc5bf23598f8703fdb6c560.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F133721_bc303cbf9fc5bf23598f8703fdb6c560.jpg&h=716120fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/133721_1a3f64bd1b3ee6c86942d8c3a4f49b66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F133721_1a3f64bd1b3ee6c86942d8c3a4f49b66.jpg&h=dbd85e50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n海雲臺市場<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/133721_06f81a6ada5619dacb0eb1526e63b43b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F133721_06f81a6ada5619dacb0eb1526e63b43b.jpg&h=1778d4ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n釜山有名的盲鰻。(車九、利狗、盲曼) 不過好貴，最低消費都 30000won，3萬W 我洗食佢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/133721_8c7936d60f671c7ccc6c1329351da123.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F133721_8c7936d60f671c7ccc6c1329351da123.jpg&h=925ef489&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5eb3d1a14f5b0db45e9500b5b40b0de18b96ea8e","tid":707132,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T06:06:38.000Z","msg":"換完錢，下個目的地就要去釜山食蟹最出名既機張市場<br />\n<br />\n呢次睇咗唔少遊記，都話呢度要講價，但啲蟹有分時令季節，唔同季節又會可以相差好遠，點先食得平唔被搵笨，就睇自己本事了。<br />\n<br />\n由海雲臺臺可以坐巴士 1003 去 (1700won) 或 39 號巴士 (1200won) 1003 就站少啲，但就算坐 39 都係唔洗一個鐘就到，睇人哋啲 blog 教坐火車，又要去 BEXCO 轉火車，仲要去到機張係唔算近個市場，坐巴士唔洗咁辛苦。<br />\n<br />\n巴士係直到機張市場門口，結果揀咗呢間，佢開完價自動減咗個價俾我睇，我再話貴，佢再減。(睇你覺得幾多先合理啦)<br />\n<br />\n或者你可以扮下嘢上咗去睇人哋張檯張單，你見到有組數字，40 就代表40000won, 100 代表10萬won。<br />\n<br />\n咁睇下人哋食幾多隻蟹，自己有個講價預算，當然睇韓國人啦，海外遊客都可能中伏多。<br />\n<br />\n呢度係預每個人一隻蟹，想食炒飯，可以加錢拎個蟹殼同啲蟹膏去炒。<br />\n<br />\n另外就係收人頭費，呢間就每人3000won，有啲可能 4000won。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/135008_2be159a1f1a0af0f71094f12c8678a51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F135008_2be159a1f1a0af0f71094f12c8678a51.jpg&h=d5c36091&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/135007_ed811727de332663e8c4bc210e4e7214.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F135007_ed811727de332663e8c4bc210e4e7214.jpg&h=a48ebca8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/135007_edd388dac8744eb5353e370c59ec544c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F135007_edd388dac8744eb5353e370c59ec544c.jpg&h=fe3c2cc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/135007_cff72e124162986166f967d1edf097d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F135007_cff72e124162986166f967d1edf097d7.jpg&h=05918b02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/135007_5f5a18aceca27185562788013102ccf7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F135007_5f5a18aceca27185562788013102ccf7.jpg&h=dc8708bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f77c3c11221ae706b5255471db1dd6d9de1512b3","tid":707132,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T06:22:17.000Z","msg":"第二間蟹店，呢度大大小小十幾間蟹店<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/141436_87e71e4a774860db4e312c8c627c18bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F141436_87e71e4a774860db4e312c8c627c18bf.jpg&h=aad6f176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無咁大隻青口肉呀？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/141437_b4a22a95b274cc3d3a247c43d7f1ff2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F141437_b4a22a95b274cc3d3a247c43d7f1ff2d.jpg&h=ec1d0693&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n海鞘綱，紅白色一個個嗰啲，切完會變咗橙色嗰兜肉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/141437_bc188d04198d3cb0c1d56e97a8f120d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F141437_bc188d04198d3cb0c1d56e97a8f120d3.jpg&h=ea237eb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n室內既海鮮市場，應該可以即買即整，有提供座位，但唔似遊客會喺度食。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/141437_5d0829da6311a0baff720fd931155695.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F141437_5d0829da6311a0baff720fd931155695.jpg&h=649fe220&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n機張市場入口<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/141437_25867dec07fe0fc5fe6c87dc511fc545.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F141437_25867dec07fe0fc5fe6c87dc511fc545.jpg&h=4bec636b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n機張市場離開的巴士站，可以坐 1003 或 39 號巴士，1003 可以坐到南浦洞。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/141438_5ec082eb0e9dcb8d714cbeac8ea08145.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F141438_5ec082eb0e9dcb8d714cbeac8ea08145.jpg&h=3345bad7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3524bb1e9e9851e6ed8d10923678da43dd2dbf96","tid":707132,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T06:40:48.000Z","msg":"由於無景點，食完蟹就坐番 1003 返去。<br />\n<br />\n天公做美，無落過雨，有時多雲，但又會散咗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/143312_4cc6d45d73b8c74f8951e60e032c92cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F143312_4cc6d45d73b8c74f8951e60e032c92cc.jpg&h=fe008b41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下晝3點就返咗去 Hostel check in，跟手沖涼洗頭瞓覺，瞓夠先出去搵食。<br />\n<br />\n海雲臺 Gunam-ro<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/143313_0395bc745497e3fa214545a1bb96daca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F143313_0395bc745497e3fa214545a1bb96daca.jpg&h=eac92fdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n路中間一段有夜市賣嘢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/143313_ff95a003ef5654844033d78771b5cc67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F143313_ff95a003ef5654844033d78771b5cc67.jpg&h=2bc7b57f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/143314_2febc8daead5fc309663dca1a8cb7a9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F143314_2febc8daead5fc309663dca1a8cb7a9f.jpg&h=c4339100&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/143314_b3cb8dedd83d94a49bea5c7786aa4f6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F143314_b3cb8dedd83d94a49bea5c7786aa4f6d.jpg&h=9123b9cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃色炸雞店<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/143314_1e51941e8742befe25e0ace515675616.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F143314_1e51941e8742befe25e0ace515675616.jpg&h=3c55de05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/143314_7b591f0cab01e98e2107582cca238433.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F143314_7b591f0cab01e98e2107582cca238433.jpg&h=b497bd36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n附近一間羊肉店<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/143315_00b0bd39896aa231f8e16b034e492036.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F143315_00b0bd39896aa231f8e16b034e492036.jpg&h=85e8f4f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n走私炸雞喺 Hostel 食，3味 18000won 包埋一枝汽水同埋一盒酸蘿蔔。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/143315_93465e2626cceb0078f761df6dbd0616.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F143315_93465e2626cceb0078f761df6dbd0616.jpg&h=791fd16d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06564e5cc61964a03cab20a0630d83c7167abf22","tid":707132,"uid":168430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:15:54.000Z","msg":"我都唔想上機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/201537_d66a9fc92eac8e8c7e527d70da2843b9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F201537_d66a9fc92eac8e8c7e527d70da2843b9.png&h=485e0679&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42efb03812d569b71a00c898c826ec3171afb860","tid":707132,"uid":117048,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:17:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e8cd09c58ad8778d5e908839fe0bbd7cd8ccedb5","tid":707132,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06564e5cc61964a03cab20a0630d83c7167abf22","tid":707132,"uid":168430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:15:54.000Z","msg":"我都唔想上機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/201537_d66a9fc92eac8e8c7e527d70da2843b9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F201537_d66a9fc92eac8e8c7e527d70da2843b9.png&h=485e0679&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:35:54.000Z","msg":"要上機喎，諗着 final call?"},{"pid":"4a7237b5a42dfb41d586adab6aef18e302e40ed7","tid":707132,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:50:41.000Z","msg":"韓狗輸波心涼一刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8bba72d8fa5c5617d9e97d12e3f1788fb216cc","tid":707132,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42efb03812d569b71a00c898c826ec3171afb860","tid":707132,"uid":117048,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:17:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:05:18.000Z","msg":"我呢次只係食，無安排景點<br />\n<br />\n因為上年先去過。"},{"pid":"97950136e2886d96a7231e149bba57961436adf6","tid":707132,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:09:16.000Z","msg":"Hostel 附近豪宅，呢邊睇既歐洲車係多過喺其他地區，Benz、寶馬、Audi 勁多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/100543_48754e7081257df24b78d954579b7394.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F100543_48754e7081257df24b78d954579b7394.jpg&h=ccbe4bc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHostel 行出去海雲臺海灘都唔駛 5分鐘<br />\n<br />\n因為仲未熱，所以唔會見好多人嚟游水，夏天就多人到爆。<br />\n<br />\n噚晚夜晚得番十七、八度，日頭只係廿三、四度，勁舒服，好過喺香港好多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/100544_4da8838175b4f82e7cd14731f8493f91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F100544_4da8838175b4f82e7cd14731f8493f91.jpg&h=bb80674a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/100544_de2f1b4fc7951237e9a45e0f886f5e16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F100544_de2f1b4fc7951237e9a45e0f886f5e16.jpg&h=49410c5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/100544_d0eb865a86ecf683f800edac0b212313.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F100544_d0eb865a86ecf683f800edac0b212313.jpg&h=df97e849&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/100544_f2bc51fe0f3a9e4d48aec5ed46d82c84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F100544_f2bc51fe0f3a9e4d48aec5ed46d82c84.jpg&h=01adb7c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37497362370bc6ed68aabc95651e9b8f9959dd3b","tid":707132,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:13:46.000Z","msg":"是日午餐<br />\n<br />\n用韓巢地圖搵咗間人參雞，係咪好出名？唔知！不過都幾多人食，亦有韓國幫襯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/101043_97f72c1e2946dfc7c219a77b61dcd3f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F101043_97f72c1e2946dfc7c219a77b61dcd3f5.jpg&h=03f5673b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點咗最貴既鮑魚參雞湯，18000won，睇相好似好大，但係我就唔飽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/101043_5fa2fbc218adc0f2aaf0027e7f3eb24a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F101043_5fa2fbc218adc0f2aaf0027e7f3eb24a.jpg&h=1b594ca8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個阿豬媽問我係咪日本人，我話係香港，佢同我講國語，講解啲鹽要放邊隻碟，骨頭放邊隻碟。"},{"pid":"3d5c63ce7702bfabf4761b14562bf4bd6819e975","tid":707132,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:52:06.000Z","msg":"食完個人參雞，就向尾浦進發。(迎月路)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/103502_782058be079da21549f980f96c3064fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F103502_782058be079da21549f980f96c3064fb.jpg&h=bc2bb02a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尾浦的郵船碼頭，可以坐遊艇出海兜個圈，分日場同夜場，要幾萬 won一個人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/103502_e09d89ee56be877bf134e890d69de316.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F103502_e09d89ee56be877bf134e890d69de316.jpg&h=fcb1544a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n望番向海雲臺<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/103502_e5aaa0219bd9ca670c11182e94e48dbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F103502_e5aaa0219bd9ca670c11182e94e48dbc.jpg&h=260e1b0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/103503_bca20ea1693c09fe13434fb70d1e076a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F103503_bca20ea1693c09fe13434fb70d1e076a.jpg&h=78d2df02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/103503_84dc192c5969fc700d2ebe0459b19f4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F103503_84dc192c5969fc700d2ebe0459b19f4d.jpg&h=a32292ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n附近的市場賣的海腸<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/103503_2645a40f14fdd772a893ab77d8229a34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F103503_2645a40f14fdd772a893ab77d8229a34.jpg&h=9a6ee821&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尾浦好多海鮮店，不過唔識韓文唔知點幫襯，提供生魚片、海參刺身同八爪魚刺身。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/103503_ddfaf1688f5a5fb3c90699fcba075c83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F103503_ddfaf1688f5a5fb3c90699fcba075c83.jpg&h=58ae9301&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尾浦去到尾一幢 Hostel (Edge 993) 好多鬼同埋有錢人嚟，好多開 Benz 同寶馬過嚟。<br />\n<a href=\"http://edge993.co.kr/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fedge993.co.kr%2F&d=nIQYG1xYKFsWK%2Fp42rwqrDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=2b790045\" target=\"_blank\">http://edge993.co.kr/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/103503_c9d813f077ed7f29197d64c332265a5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F103503_c9d813f077ed7f29197d64c332265a5b.jpg&h=c3fd79db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/103504_a666b539d26f879fac6a2f2411aceca9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F103504_a666b539d26f879fac6a2f2411aceca9.jpg&h=944e01af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a11da0f3feb3f064e1661879330912d614091bfd","tid":707132,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T03:05:01.000Z","msg":"尾浦~青沙浦舊鐵路<br />\n<br />\n天氣唔係太熱，又太陽又有雲遮咗，行呢段路幾舒服<br />\n<br />\n好多人都專登行同影相，由呢度行到去青沙浦，連綠2 巴士都唔駛搭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/103501_fc7fa94e37d38d16e7d1dc8ac0242a0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F103501_fc7fa94e37d38d16e7d1dc8ac0242a0c.jpg&h=41fb4d0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/110351_4639d6102b00ba146dfea92161030baf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F110351_4639d6102b00ba146dfea92161030baf.jpg&h=b1323fd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/110352_da01d64024d1caf51ca6a9a8d1fac965.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F110352_da01d64024d1caf51ca6a9a8d1fac965.jpg&h=03b6354e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/110352_9c9fbc72658c4784b4c23b02e41ced5c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F110352_9c9fbc72658c4784b4c23b02e41ced5c.jpg&h=dee9c710&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/110352_6526edf8555ee1dc407b1e52ec06a7d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F110352_6526edf8555ee1dc407b1e52ec06a7d0.jpg&h=9b177bfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/110352_86f7017643f57bac2061c3391fcaf8f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F110352_86f7017643f57bac2061c3391fcaf8f4.jpg&h=08aca2c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/110353_33ec04df084699a3e3a2ce4b9351ace6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F110353_33ec04df084699a3e3a2ce4b9351ace6.jpg&h=aca95cb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/110353_5fec29de088c1a7e7996150a793cdcc9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F110353_5fec29de088c1a7e7996150a793cdcc9.jpg&h=06857aba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/110353_9f12d4ffaa910900d0adfe10b3a1b48d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F110353_9f12d4ffaa910900d0adfe10b3a1b48d.jpg&h=b09000cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e7fe9dcde3c20d37eeac95bc80f644d494342920","tid":707132,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T03:13:20.000Z","msg":"其實行過去都唔覺好遠，因為唔洗上山落斜<br />\n<br />\n韓國政府保育都幾好，雖然條鐵路晨早無咗火車行，但仍然保留着平交道。(雖然沒作用)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/110931_cd292e9c982efbb20fe3777aef925408.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F110931_cd292e9c982efbb20fe3777aef925408.jpg&h=cf0ee582&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲訊號燈仲 Keep 着。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/110931_f3a476609a0722398c2b4213d61d5f03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F110931_f3a476609a0722398c2b4213d61d5f03.jpg&h=8fddd2e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n終於到達青沙浦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/110930_ecfac95f6cb1eddec40aae5ef85510c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F110930_ecfac95f6cb1eddec40aae5ef85510c9.jpg&h=14218e8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/110929_fc3091e73daf7705e717f